# CrewMarkdown — GitHub Copilot Instructions

This project uses `.crewmarkdown/00-objectives.md` for workflow routing.

## On Any Software Request

1. Read `codebase-map.md` if exists (file tree)
2. Read `.crewmarkdown/00-objectives.md` → find matching objective
3. Check `.crewmarkdown/custom/<phase>.md` for overrides
4. Follow objective's procedure → produce artifacts
5. Write log to `.crewmarkdown/logs/<yyyy>/<MM>/<dd>/<HHmmss>/<chat-slug>-[<HHmmss>]/<role>.md` (derive `<chat-slug>` from request text)
6. Update `.crewmarkdown/state/workflow.json`

## Key Files
- `.crewmarkdown/00-objectives.md` — routing table + objective index
- `.crewmarkdown/state/workflow.json` — current state
- `codebase-map.md` — file tree (generated)
